title.rendered: How Amazon Makes Money with Robin Gaster of Incumetrics

content.rendered:
Podcast: Play in new window | Download (Duration: 24:37 — 22.5MB)

Subscribe: Spotify | Email | RSS

Podcast (10k-podcast): Play in new window | Download (Duration: 24:37 — 22.5MB)

Subscribe: Spotify | Email | TuneIn | RSS

Today we are still with Robin Gaster, he will talk about how Amazon is currently making its money. We will also talk about how Amazon reports its revenue which saves them a ton of money.

 

You’ll Learn:

  • The most profitable area of Amazon
  • How the changes within Amazon affects the third-party marketplace sellers
  • How Amazon could lose 40B USD as a 1P seller
  • The notion of brand in Amazon
